transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Namaste ma'am, main Vikas bol raha hoon.
Customer: Ji ji.
Executive: Vikas bol raha hoon. Keh raha hoon ki ma'am abhi call kiya tha kya aapne 9696 wale number pe?
Customer: Woh galti se kar diya tha maine.
Executive: Achha galti se lag gaya tha. Toh main close kar de raha hoon ticket, theek hai na? Koi ticket generate ho jaata hai jaise hi aap click karte ho.
Customer: Actually main woh customer ko call kar rahi thi, aapne woh bola tha na Ram unko, toh maine galti se woh call list mein aapka number dikha.
Executive: Nahi nahi, koi issue nahi hai, koi issue nahi hai. Main isko close kar de raha hoon, theek hai? Feedback jayega, feedback mein yes kar dijiyega ma'am, theek hai?
Customer: Hmm.
